# {{.Name}}

Scaffolded by [hex](https://github.com/jordanbrauer/hex).

## Layout

```
{{.Name}}/
├── cmd/{{.BinaryName}}/main.go   # entry point
├── provider/                     # service providers (boot order matters)
├── domain/                       # your business logic
├── infrastructure/               # driver adapters (SQL repos, HTTP clients)
├── cli/root.go                   # cobra command tree
├── build/                        # build metadata
├── config/defaults/              # embedded TOML defaults
{{- if ne .Dialect "none" }}
├── db/migrations/                # SQL migrations (embed.FS)
{{- end }}
└── Makefile
```

## Running

```bash
go mod tidy
go run ./cmd/{{.BinaryName}}
```

## Generators

Add code with the `hex` CLI (from the project root):

```bash
hex make:provider payments        # provider/payments.go, wired into boot.go
hex make:domain user              # domain/user/{user,repository,service,errors}.go
hex make:migration create_users   # db/migrations/<ts>_create_users.{up,down}.sql
```

## Build

```bash
make build          # produces bin/{{.BinaryName}} with ldflags-populated version info
```
